<?xml-stylesheet type="text/xsl" href="../assets/xml/rss.xsl" media="all"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom"><channel><title>写程序的龙龙 (Posts about pexpect)</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/</link><description></description><atom:link href="https://codinglonglong.github.io/categories/pexpect.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"></atom:link><language>en</language><lastBuildDate>Sat, 30 Dec 2017 09:31:44 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>Nikola (getnikola.com)</generator><docs>http://blogs.law.harvard.edu/tech/rss</docs><item><title>使用pexpect远程登录SSH</title><link>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/shi-yong-pexpectyuan-cheng-deng-lu-ssh/</link><dc:creator>龙龙</dc:creator><description>&lt;div&gt;&lt;p&gt;pexpect可以自动和命令行程序进行交互，在系统部署和测试的时候非常好用。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;以远程登录SSH并执行命令为例&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;pre class="literal-block"&gt;
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; emacs dparkstarter.py
import pexpect

ip = "192.168.1.211"
name = "long"
child = pexpect.spawn('ssh  %s@%s' % (name, ip))
child.expect('$')
child.sendline('python dparkslave.py')
child.interact()
&amp;gt;&amp;gt; python dparkstarter.py
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;p&gt;程序可以自动登录SSH，然后执行python dparkslave.py这条命令。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description><category>pexpect</category><category>Python</category><guid>https://codinglonglong.github.io/posts/shi-yong-pexpectyuan-cheng-deng-lu-ssh/</guid><pubDate>Wed, 16 Sep 2015 06:55:48 GMT</pubDate></item></channel></rss>